      <h1 style="margin-top:10px">How to run a handicap doubles tournament</h1>
      <p class="lede">A club tournament where only the best four have a chance is a tournament most of your members will sit out. A handicap event flips that: everyone has a genuine shot, every match is tense, and the whole club takes part. Here is how to run one.</p>
